@startuml
title 이메일 인증

actor User
participant AuthController
participant AuthService
participant EmailService
participant PendingAuthRepository

User -> AuthController : POST /auth/request-verification\n{email}
AuthController -> AuthService : sendVerificationEmail(email)

AuthService -> EmailService : sendVerificationCode(email)
EmailService --> AuthService : verificationCode

AuthService -> PendingAuthRepository : save(email, verificationCode)

AuthService --> User : HTTP 200 OK (이메일 확인 요청)
@enduml